*** Wizard News ***

Welcome, wizard! Here are some things to know:

RECENT CHANGES:
- Orc Fortress quest added (room/orc_fortress/) -- 12-room dungeon
  connected from room/fortress.c. Includes boss encounter in the
  throne room.
- Runtime error logging enabled in obj/master.c -- errors are now
  written to log/debug.log for easier debugging.
- Wizard level check relaxed in obj/leo.c.
- Double login prompt bug fixed in obj/player.c.

WIZARD COMMANDS:
  Type 'help' to see wizard-specific commands. Key commands include:
  clone <file>    - create an instance of an object
  destruct <obj>  - destroy an object
  goto <place>    - teleport to a room or player
  load <file>     - load/compile an LPC file
  update <file>   - reload a modified object
  stat <player>   - view a player's stats
  trans <player>  - teleport a player to you
  ed <file>       - edit a file with the in-game editor

BUILDING:
  Room files go in room/, monsters in monsters/, objects in obj/.
  See doc/build/ for building guides on rooms, monsters, weapons,
  and armour. New public areas should be documented in the project
  README under "Custom Additions".
